title: El color de las nubes 1997 [PAZ]
description:
The Color of the Clouds 1997

Language: Spanish
Subtitle: English (.srt)

Lola's son is trying to take her country house from her but she refuses to leave. Meanwhile a supposed Bosnian refugee being looked after by Lola is actually Bartolome, who has run away from home. A romance develops between Lola's lawyer, Valerio and her niece Clementina, and Colo the local fisherman finds a consignment of drugs and decides to sell them to raise money to save Lola's house.
